An implementation of the model object 'Component Classifier'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Classifier Feature
  • Owned Member
  • Owned Mode
  • Owned Mode Transition
  • Owned Processor Port
  • Owned Internal Event
  • No Flows
  • No Modes
